OL,6,F"This was a very distressing incident
OL,7,Fand our thoughts are with the victims,
OL,8,Ftheir family and everyone impacted by
OL,9,Fwhat has happened.
OL,11,F"I am aware that there is footage of
OL,12,Fthe incident currently circulating on
OL,13,Fsocial media and would ask that this
OL,14,Fis removed to avoid contempt of court
OL,15,Fand distress to those affected.
OL,17,F"I would also ask that people do not
OL,18,Fspeculate while there is a police
